message.body: Hey Liza it is Jamie from NIH. Did you get Dr. Jarcho's email this morning?
Yes I did, we are in touch. Thank you!
Of course. Please let me know if you are around and free later... I would be happy to chat or meet as well! Are you in Maryland?
I am, I'm staying with a friend who lives right off campus. I am going to see if I can get in, and if not, meet with a few people off-campus.
Wonderful! Please let me know if you need anything.
